{"tid":2012583,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"PK鄧聽日會去元朗","createTime":"2020-05-11T17:17:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T18:43:35.000Z","uid":211994,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1229c2e3888a253c555c17b52f4c88d1051ed35c","tid":2012583,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T17:17:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/yuenlongox/36942\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyuenlongox%2F36942&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HcbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=0f29b877\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/yuenlongox/36942</a><br />\n<br />\n🚨 #Admin呼籲 🚨<br />\n由於今日朝早1000 於橋樂坊元朗政府合署將會舉行第四次元朗區議會會議 <br />\n到時Pk Tang將會親臨元朗區議會接受質詢‼️<br />\n<br />\n預計到時橋樂坊大橋街市附近將會有一定狗力進駐 因此我地在此呼籲各位街坊踴躍報哨‼️<br />\n同時亦都需要注意附近隨時有便衣狗蹤影‼️<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以用少少時間記低大橋街市附近道路名稱 例如橋樂坊安寧路壽富街福德街同樂街 等等<br />\n<br />\nAdmin在此感謝各位街坊配合‼️<br />\n希望大家可以踴躍報哨‼️<br />\n@yuenlongoxreport_bot"},{"pid":"787c3424bf6b0ff2be10193b26a825158e2725c2","tid":2012583,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T17:20:04.000Z","msg":"議員又要俾PK鄧撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53c7e3c797e762e7256472cb2c040b024978f5fb","tid":2012583,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T17:21:27.000Z","msg":"軍政府落場教做人道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad6b09fc22ca8e780b1d12ab5d1a1881c7ad10fc","tid":2012583,"uid":168389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T17:21:38.000Z","msg":"走場狗"},{"pid":"0107a97caa392d8378598ce70f3a90e21a9bfa47","tid":2012583,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T17:28:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e1d01e1662c1690e0a3eac7a6b4b0db15400e86","tid":2012583,"uid":127929,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T17:54:05.000Z","msg":"<